VotingModuleTest
├── when initializing
│   └── it should set max points and strategies
├── when casting a direct vote
│   └── it should record vote and update distribution
├── when casting a vote with signature
│   └── it should verify signature and emit VoteCast
├── when casting batch votes
│   └── it should record all votes and emit BatchVotesCast
├── when recasting a vote
│   └── it should replace the previous vote distribution
├── when replaying a nonce
│   └── it should revert with NonceAlreadyUsed
├── when using an invalid signature
│   └── it should revert with InvalidSignature
├── when voting with zero power
│   └── it should record vote with zero effect
├── when exceeding max points
│   └── it should revert with ExceedsMaxPoints
├── when all points are zero
│   └── it should revert with ZeroVotePoints
├── when validating a signature
│   ├── it should return true for valid signature
│   └── it should return false for wrong voter
├── when querying voting power
│   └── it should return correct power per token holdings
├── when advancing to a new cycle
│   └── it should reset vote tracking for new cycle
└── when skipping nonces
    └── it should allow non-sequential nonce usage